Text: Is this the 2nd Umineko fighting game?

A dōjin 2D fighting game produced by 07th Expansion titled Ōgon Musōkyoku, Golden Fantasia was released on December 31, 2010 at Comiket 79. A sequel, tentatively titled Ōgon Musōkyoku 2 Golden Fantasia 2 is scheduled for release at Comiket 81 in December 2011. In addition, an Xbox 360 port of the original game developed by Alchemist will be released on October 6, 2011 under the title Ōgon Musōkyoku X Golden Fantasia X)
